WEBVTT

00:00:29.982 --> 00:00:31.812
Aquele louco de chapéu...

00:00:32.740 --> 00:00:33.900
era eu.

00:00:33.924 --> 00:00:34.984
(Risos)

00:00:35.008 --> 00:00:36.649
(Aplausos)

00:00:36.673 --> 00:00:39.649
(Vivas)

00:00:45.085 --> 00:00:48.161
E a resposta para aquela pergunta,
surpreendentemente,

00:00:48.185 --> 00:00:49.344
é "sim".

00:00:49.368 --> 00:00:50.518
(Risos)

00:00:51.224 --> 00:00:53.503
Cresci assistindo luta livre profissional

00:00:53.527 --> 00:00:54.705
com meu pai.

00:00:55.252 --> 00:00:57.385
Como ele, eu amava tudo sobre luta livre:

00:00:57.409 --> 00:00:59.453
o espetáculo, as habilidades atléticas,

00:00:59.477 --> 00:01:00.717
o drama.